						               													<description>Lion's Wrath; Northern Army List&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Originally scheduled to be released at Xmas'13, the &amp;quot;army list&amp;quot; is a new format replacing the last two unpublished Field Guides prior to Dream Pod 9's announced rules revamp sometime in late 2014 or early 2015.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Unlike the full Field Guides for the New Coalition and Allied Southern Territories the army list formatting does not contain any fluff chapters or a full vehicle compendium.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This book is available only in an electronic format.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;From the back cover;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;TN 1951&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Northern Army List&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Includes new vehicles, datacards, how to build your army, updated combat groups and threat values. Plus options for the five Northern factions or a generic force:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;- Northern Guard (NG)&amp;#10;- Northern Lights Confederacy Armed Forces (NAF)&amp;#10;- United Mercantile Federation Army (UMFA)&amp;#10;- Western Frontier Protectorate Army (WFPA)&amp;#10;- Northern Territorial Reserves (NTR)&amp;#10;- Generic Northern Army&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This 54 page book is an Army List for use with a copy of the most current Heavy Gear Blitz! Core Rulebook. Miniatures, six-sided dice, and a measuring tape are required for play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;For two or more players, ages 8 and up.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
